01:11:43.300 --> 01:11:44.732
[sighs]

01:11:46.269 --> 01:11:48.870
I'm sure you noticed
      that Rachel has a...

01:11:49.973 --> 01:11:51.105
type.

01:11:52.309 --> 01:11:54.609
I mean, you must have.

01:11:54.711 --> 01:11:59.013
