-Scott would never--
        -Well, maybe not.

01:12:06.756 --> 01:12:09.457
But Rachel would.

01:12:09.559 --> 01:12:13.961
She has some [chuckles]
      serious daddy issues.

01:12:15.065 --> 01:12:18.399
Ah... works for me.

