<i> The new office going well?</i>

01:20:06.269 --> 01:20:09.537
-Yeah. It's perfect.
             <i> -Good.</i>

01:20:09.639 --> 01:20:12.006
<i> Look, I just wanted to say</i>
      <i> I'm really glad that</i>

01:20:12.108 --> 01:20:14.642
<i> we could find a solution</i>
       <i> to keeping you on.</i>

01:20:14.744 --> 01:20:16.977
<i> InHabit is now trending</i>
        <i> because of you.</i>

01:20:17.079 --> 01:20:18.546
[Eric laughs]

01:20:18.648 --> 01:20:20.981
<i> Oh, that reminds me, um,</i>

01:20:21.083 --> 01:20:23.751
<i> I wanted to talk to you</i>
    <i> about our presentation.</i>

