I wish I could, but

01:20:26.756 --> 01:20:28.389
I've got lunch plans
         with the baby.

01:20:28.491 --> 01:20:31.492
<i> Yeah, I know. Um, I figured</i>
      <i> I'd give it a shot.</i>

